com.google.api.ads.dfp.lib

Class DfpServiceFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.api.ads.dfp.lib.DfpServiceFactory

  • public final class DfpServiceFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    The DfpServiceFactory generates service stubs with an Axis EngineConfiguration which maps the HTTP transport to the class DfpHttpSender. If a custom client configuration must be deployed, there is an example client-config.wsdd included in this distribution, which when included in the classpath and when user.useClasspathClientConfig == true, will override this class' EngineConfiguration. Not setting the DfpHttpSender to the HTTP transport will result in the loss of functionality in SOAP XML logging and ServiceAccountant abilities.
    Author:
    api.arogal@gmail.com (Adam Rogal)
